longBusinessSummary: Modern Mobility Aids, Inc. operates in the telehealth and telemedicine industry. It operates a telehealth platform incorporating AI and IOT to get access to healthcare regardless of location and financial status. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Brampton, Canada.
